description:
Doree feels a feeling she hasn’t felt in a while, and Kate is sore from sitting too much. Then, listeners share their thoughts on micro-blading, full-butted underwear for flat-butted listeners, and mindless munching. Plus, a listener calls in with a work meet-cute.
